form.b-grist-create-form
  .row
    select.col-md-3.b-grist-create-form__lexer(name="lexer", ui-select2="{ allowClear: true}", ng-model="select2", placeholder="Guess")
      option
      option(value="JavaScript") JavaScript
      option(value="CoffeeScript") CoffeeScript
      option(value="Ruby") Ruby
      option(value="PHP") PHP
      option(value="C#") C#

    .col-md-9
      |  Guess | Text | Python | JavaScript | Ruby | CSS | HTML | Django/Jinja (press Ctrl-J to select from keyboard)

  .row
    .col-md-12
      textarea.form-control.b-grist-create-form__source(name="source")

  .row
    .col-md-3
      button.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary(type="submit") Create
      | (or press Ctrl-Enter)